title: Bug 4121: JarExporter causes out of Sync (1GILQD5)
description: Bug 4121: JarExporter causes out of Sync (1GILQD5)
OB: When using the JarExporter module, the exported jar file includes itself, leading to an out of sync error.
EB: The exported jar file should not include itself to avoid the out of sync error.
SR:
To reproduce the issue, follow these steps:
1. Use the JarExporter module to export a jar file.
2. Check the contents of the exported jar file and confirm if it includes itself.
